{"tid":800240,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【睇《延禧》學到咩】清代後宮鬥餐死 美國人已經炒股搞發明","createTime":"2018-08-30T16:44:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-01T01:28:23.000Z","uid":28765,"like":61,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"1ea60650856d7bfc4950c7234387cf390d7341d8","tid":800240,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T16:44:57.000Z","msg":"人生如戲，還是戲如人生？內地近年流行拍攝宮鬥劇，一套《延禧攻略》就看得一眾大媽大叔如癡如醉。有網友就做過歷史考證，發現在清代後宮妃嬪爭寵鬥得不可開交、一眾大臣被皇上怒斥為狗奴才的同一時間裏，身處地球另一面的美國人，已經開始炒股票、搞發明，食「大茶飯」了。睇《延禧》的同時，應該會學到點東西吧？！<br />\n<br />\n例如，乾隆五十七年（1792），紐約證券交易所正式成立，成為美國資本主義的象徵。道光十七年（1837），美國消費日用品公司「寶潔」P&amp;G成立，該公司至今在全球80多個國家設有工廠或分公司，所經營的品牌產品暢銷180多個國家和地區；到道光二十九年（1849年），生物科研製藥公司「輝瑞」Pfizer成立，該公司1998年推出威而鋼（Viagra），造福無數飽受陽痿之苦的男士。<br />\n同治八年（1869年），銀行控股公司「高盛」Goldman Sachs成立，該司發展至今，已成為向全球客戶提供廣泛的投資、諮詢和金融服務的跨國集團，同同時影響世界經濟。光緒六年（1880年），攝影器材及菲林沖曬公司「柯達」Kodak，對往後百年的攝影技術發展具有深遠影響。光緒十二年至光緒三十四年（1886年至1908年），「強生」Johnson &amp; Johnson、「可口可樂」Coca-cola、「通用電氣」GE、「吉列」Gillette、福特汽車「Ford」等這些大品牌相繼出現，時至今日仍在主導或影響着全球人們的日常生活。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180830/large/1535637335_4b24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180830%2Flarge%2F1535637335_4b24.jpg&h=7285e8bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n清代後宮妃嬪爭寵，那邊廂美國人已經成立證券交易所，發展金融經濟了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180831/58626676\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180831%2F58626676&d=SnJ3DapagYs6fShdi%2BcBe8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=e08e3839\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180831%2F58626676&h=3482456d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180831/58626676</a>"},{"pid":"20c48500621fe269ad30a08cea6bf680f3bebdd0","tid":800240,"uid":29702,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T16:49:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5799e5eb997e4b38b938415850c3b08a89660c90","tid":800240,"uid":118758,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T16:52:13.000Z","msg":"從來唔睇清朝劇 再加上仲要大陸拍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c35b3f05684bd5dc31e8bd2269bd09d3afc844f","tid":800240,"uid":77788,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T16:53:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"77531b517769e3cf68f83b2643232269af7b60e4","tid":800240,"uid":54371,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T16:58:12.000Z","msg":"嘩<br />\n一句 &quot;有網友就做過歷史考證&quot; 就成個post抄晒落去<br />\n班記者係唔係少少羞恥心都冇"},{"pid":"e5166000821389ca49b7e00ea276518d4f93b4a9","tid":800240,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"5799e5eb997e4b38b938415850c3b08a89660c90","tid":800240,"uid":118758,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T16:52:13.000Z","msg":"從來唔睇清朝劇 再加上仲要大陸拍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T17:01:10.000Z","msg":"X2 on9先睇"},{"pid":"e75e88b209bde1da22c171324b9270a22aa6ff98","tid":800240,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T17:15:45.000Z","msg":"果時大清唔係有和坤，胡雪巖呢啲政商天才咩？"},{"pid":"3823362179bd6bf0970b1301451edb1044e0fcd8","tid":800240,"uid":50457,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T23:48:56.000Z","msg":"集權中央點會有進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58daa33fb39cb00b9b16790f176369772bcadec1","tid":800240,"uid":47674,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T00:41:45.000Z","msg":"同一時期清朝發明咗象牙球、肉形石、翠玉白菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93d230a423cc0f55c1b2be8dada45b9ccc854310","tid":800240,"uid":30145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T00:42:57.000Z","msg":"做咩又出多次段文<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm